title: MisterMusic Show 354 - indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 354 [120 minutes] 192kbpsMP3



On the show this week, new music from The Helio Sequence,
Cheers Elephant, and another new song from the latest album by The Wombats.
And we travel back to May 1994 for an alternative rock hit that spent 3 weeks at number 1 for the 'Oldie of the Week'. 
It's over 5 decades of classic hits broadcasting weekly- The MisterMusic Show.

The MisterMusic Show is heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
